'''Mɔʋ''' kɛna tɔɔnasɩ nzɩ sɩkɛ pe yɔ sɩ-taa nakɛyɛ. Pahayɩɣ-kʋ hɔɔlɩŋ weyi ɛ-taa soŋgaɣ nɛ niikaɣ pɛwɛɛ yɔ. Papɩzɩɣ pahayɩ-kʋ ɖɔɖɔ hɔɔlɩŋ weyi ɛ-taa niikaɣ nɛ wɩsɩ pɛwɛ pazɩ pazɩ yɔ. Pahayɩɣ mɔʋ fɛɛŋ taa, pɩkɩlɩna ɖenɖe lɩm wɛ fɛndɛlɛɛɛ yɔ. Payaɣ pɩ-tɛ hayɩm se mɔʋ ɛjɛŋ. Pahayɩɣ-kʋ ki-pe yɔɔ. Kɩ-taa n̄ɩm ɖɔ pɩdɩɩfɛyɩ.

[[File:Oryza sativa.JPG|thumb|Oryza sativa]]
 
Mɔʋ wɛna hɩla ndɩ ndɩ. Payaɣ [[Aazii tɛtʋ wandamm]] taa mɔʋ se "''Oryza sativa''", payaa Afrika wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʋyɛ taa mɔʋ se "''Oryza glaberrima''" yaa "Casamance" mɔʋ. 

[[File:Terrace field yunnan china denoised.jpg|thumb|Terrace field yunnan china denoised]]

Ɛyaa sakɩyɛ sɔɔlɩ mɔʋ pɩkɩlɩ tɔɔnasɩ lɛɛsɩ, kɔzɩ kɔzɩ [[Amerika nɛ hadɛ tɛtʋ (Amérique du Sud)|Amerika nɛ hadɛ kiŋ]] tɛtʋ taa n̄ɩma nɛ [[Afrɩka tɛtʋ wandamm (Continent africain)|Afrika]] nɛ Aasii pɛ-tɛtʋ taa n̄ɩma. Mɔʋ kɛna kajalaɣ tɔɔnaɣ ŋga ɛyaa kɩlɩɣ tɔɔʋ kedeŋa yɔɔ cɩnɛ yɔ. Pʋ-yɔɔ pakɩlɩɣ-kʋ hayʋʋ kedeŋa yɔɔ cɩnɛ. Huŋ nʋmɔʋ taa lɛ, saamɩla wayɩ lɛ, mɔʋ tɩŋɩɣna tɔɔnasɩ pe n̄ɩnzɩ ɛsɩndaa. [[Siini]] nɛ [[Ɛɛndɩ]] nɛ [[Sapɔŋ]] pa-ajɛya taa pakɩlɩɣ mɔʋ tɔɔʋ.

